l in some big guns and fight over mobs with them, we left.  We tried again later and similar thing happened.<br>
<br>
While I doubt that the reservation system will ever be reinstated or if it would work if it was, the current system (if there even is one) sure the hell doesn't work.  50+ characters should not have to leave and join uber guilds or beg for scraps from them in order to hunt in the planes once and a while.  Perhaps if someone kept a calendar and guilds communicated with one another more and tried to share planes with each other, more people would get what they want and we would all be much happier.  Even a FCFS system would be better than allowing biggest bully on the block to take over everything.  Take a look around sometime, uber guilds... you aren't the only ones in Quellious.  The person who just SoWed, healed, buffed, ported, rezzed, or guided you (often at no charge) may just be from a guild like mine and we have every right to be there and have some of the same opportunities as you all do.<br>
<br>
Juror Beaumains<br>
Shaman of The Tribunal<br>
High Elder / events coordinator, Healers United <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub54.ezboard.com/uraalf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raalf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Corpse Artist </span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#00CCFF>(3/5/01 2:20:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bullied out of Fear</span><hr size=1> I can't really speak of the specific date you're talking of, cause I wasn't there. I DO know some friends I have in HU have contacted me and asked me &quot;wtf man?&quot; And I'll tell you what I've told them:<br>
