Wraith has more or less gone FFA, as has the rest of the server, whether they wanted to or not. Remember the &quot;reservation system&quot;? where is it now. GONE. Nothing is left, because of ASSHOLES, both guilded, and nonguilded. Know why Pantera etc took down the board? because of in-game AND out-game harassment! Can you imagine someone threatening to kick your ass over a spawn? I don't blame him. They've tried their damndest to stay afloat among this mess, but getting refused to groups cause of being a moderator? Hell, I even got a wierd IM one day from a &quot;KefkahKaos&quot; on AOL. He stated my full name and said hello. I don't know if it was the real one or not, but regardless, it was an odd feeling, when none of my friends would fess up. I don't really want someone pulling stunts like that on me either! I'm a moderater here, but if you screw with me, I'll quietly tell the other moderators I'm deleting yer posts and banning you. If that doesn't stop the posts, I'll ban IP/domain. And if that doesn't stop ya, I'll just report the traffic as harassment to your respective authorites.<br>
<br>
Yes there's hostility now. Is it my fault? Wraith's fault? Vis's fault? DB's fault? Goin downhill now, departures come every day of people quitting. More will follow. about 35% of the best players of Quellious are gone. By best, I mean the honest, fun, PLAYERS. Not the ones who've made EQ their life. Honestly, I hope Verant pulls the plug, and makes somepeople go back hardcore to RL. I'd like to see a 2 month downtime, JUST to see who comes back, who doesn't care, and who commits suicide cause EQ is out of their lives for a few months. Did you know that really might happen? Stop getting pissed cause of this crap.<br>
<br>
Get in groups, go fletch arrows for tanks, go port newbies to Toxx, go megabuff crocs in Oasis, SURELY you can find something to do. I've invited someone who's nonguilded on EVERY raid i've been in! I take my FRIENDS. If I remember you being a jerk, you're not goin. I have yet to be kicked out of a group cause of my guild, and I think it's mostly cause I'm known for being me. I always answer EVERY tell. I never refuse 1 person, cause of exp. (well, except for 1 time... hehe sorry Docc!)<br>
<br>
What choice is left but FFA now? Feel free to tell me. I do NOT like FFA. It makes my guildmates get pissed when I can't be around for kills that are going on NOW cause I have work etc. I'd rather know a week or so in advance, &quot;Trak on Thursday&quot; than log on and get &quot;oshit, someone go get raalf, port him in, we got under 20 min before VM breaks past the reets!&quot;<br>
